{"tid":1632062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本台記者被懷疑汽油彈擲中　記協嚴厲譴責暴力行為","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:43.000Z","uid":70238,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"28e5ead2c40b94e8a4958b55fd1f933410d5c4f5","tid":1632062,"uid":70238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484674-20191007.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484674-20191007.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=5df6c154\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484674-20191007.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=18525246\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484674-20191007.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n唉！！！"},{"pid":"c6bc7d671d5f1dc35ad8220cf6b5435d4a28dff6","tid":1632062,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"687a193cdd45361048cf0c3fcef7ca692901da00","tid":1632062,"uid":141879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"冷處理，集中番抗爭到"},{"pid":"a9ba2f4debff73c1005bd459dfd61c4348e37f4d","tid":1632062,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"[遍地落區公投] 連登已被嚴重滲透，任何風向公投都唔應該再係連登搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec909890514ece7012ff7abb527822141adbe9ce","tid":1632062,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"bc210e04ac2f117920d86448cb641652cca95e96","tid":1632062,"uid":106604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"2b8c0e2ae1f5a18650ecebbe5d631f07d0e5047d","tid":1632062,"uid":59868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"有咩好唉，記協係要出黎譴責架啦<br />\n無論汽油彈，定係橡膠子彈，催淚彈定水炮車<br />\n射中記者就會譴責，譴完咪等下次譴責囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fdaba2ba87097d56b3df42248031550fb9564b","tid":1632062,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b8c0e2ae1f5a18650ecebbe5d631f07d0e5047d","tid":1632062,"uid":59868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"有咩好唉，記協係要出黎譴責架啦<br />\n無論汽油彈，定係橡膠子彈，催淚彈定水炮車<br />\n射中記者就會譴責，譴完咪等下次譴責囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"fdc595eb0b9efc0cccb68fbaf434bb0f36d8963e","tid":1632062,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"對唔住，會留意！"},{"pid":"92897d0ef724d8899267c0c55a9d2b3bdd3a4547","tid":1632062,"uid":2218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"我代佢地Say Sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed2539d6b949e59b50aec0302fd091413710c61","tid":1632062,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"今日風向：勇武退場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ded50ce88ba487a60310fabbc1543f826b51324e","tid":1632062,"uid":306172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"其實你地知唔知乜撚野叫成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}